prodNameC: 美堅迪爾埃亞硝酸鹽試劑
ingredientsDesc:
Nitrite-Detect Reagent: Contains 2 x 500 mL of N-1-naphthylethylenediamine and sulfanilamide in an acidic solution.
Nitrite-Detect 200μg/mL Control: Contains 1 x 25 mL of 200 μg/mL nitrite in an aqueous solution.
Nitrite-Detect Calibrator Kit: Contains 1 x 25 mL of negative nitrite calibrator and 1 x 25 mL of 500μg/mL nitrite in an aqueous solution.
Nitrite-Detect Control Kit: Contains 1 x 25 mL of Negative Control (375μg/mL nitrite) and 1 x 25 mL of Positive Control (625μg/mL nitrite) in an aqueous solution.
applicantName: 杏全實業股份有限公司
efficacy: 以亞硝酸鹽化合物檢測尿液中的摻雜物。
